Item
An Item is a object that can be transported by a Passenger of an elevator.
Load
A load is a object that can be transported by elevator such as items or passengers.
LogFormatter
A custom formatter for our log files.
MoveDirection

Describes passengers exiting the elevator at a specific floor.
RNG

Simulation
Contains all information needed to run a simulation and handles the basic simulation logic.
SimulationAlreadyInitializedException
An exception that is thrown when a simulation has been initialized and it is attempted to initialize it again.
SimulationAlreadyRunningException
An exception that is thrown when the simulation is already running but it is attempted to start it again.
SimulationNotInitializedException
An exception that is thrown when a simulation is run without being initialized first.
